1. Imam *torbu* sa sobom. (I have a bag with me.)
2. Molim te, donesi mi *torbu* iz sobe. (Please bring me the bag from the room.)
3. Sinoć sam kupila tri nove *torbe*. (Last night I bought three new bags.)
4. On je prenosio *torbe* sa pijace. (He was carrying bags from the market.)
5. *Torba* je pala na pod. (The bag fell on the floor.)
6. Nisam siguran gde sam ostavio svoju *torbu*. (I'm not sure where I left my bag.)
7. Ova *torba* je preteška za mene. (This bag is too heavy for me.)
8. Moramo pronaći način da spakujemo sve u jednu *torbu*. (We need to find a way to pack everything in one bag.)
9. Naše dete je izgubilo *torbu* u školi. (Our child lost their bag at school.)
10. Molim vas, stavite moju knjigu u *torbu*. (Please put my book in the bag.)